                </strong>
              </p>

              <div className="bg-status-success/10 border border-status-success rounded-button p-4 mt-4">
                <p className="text-sm text-status-success font-medium">
                  ✅ Automatic backups every 30 seconds
                  <br />
                  ✅ Sync across all your devices
